--- Prior-work references (design-only, no bundled code) ---

This project's data contract (notably the Physical, Cognitive, and
PerceptionEvent schemas in src/erre_sandbox/schemas.py) was informed by
the design of CSDG (Cognitive State Diary Generator) by mikotomiura,
MIT-licensed at
https://github.com/mikotomiura/cognitive-state-diary-generator.
The shape of HumanCondition, CharacterState, and DailyEvent in CSDG
inspired our Physical, Cognitive, and PerceptionEvent schemas; no code
is reused verbatim. Specific pattern adoptions are documented in the
repository file `.steering/20260418-schemas-freeze/decisions.md` (this
steering log is kept in the repository and is not bundled with released
wheels / sdists).
